#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:64
#: 0c0e1ab7a7924452aedbd2c5a50474e1
msgid ""
"We represent node states with three Boolean indicator vectors :math:`h, w, r"
" \\in \\{0,1\\}^N`. Let :math:`N(i)` be the neighbor set of node :math:`i`. "
"The update at discrete step :math:`k` is performed in the following stages "
"(matching the reference implementation):"
msgstr ""
"我们代表三个布尔指标矢量的节点状态:`h, w, r\\ in \\{0, 1\\}^n'。 让:math:`N(i)'成为邻接的一组节点:`i'。 "
"`k'分以下几个阶段进行(匹配参考执行):"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:66
#: fbd6db9c032e42cab49467af55d8cadb
msgid ""
":math:`h_i=1` indicates node :math:`i` is ``infected`` or ``weakened``; "
":math:`h_i=0` indicates ``susceptible`` or ``recovered``."
msgstr ":math:`h i=1'表示节点:`i'表示\"感染\"或\"微弱\";`h i=0'表示\"疑似\"或\"恢复\"."

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:67
#: b0d6c0b5a6514085b239f487fb3e1262
msgid ""
":math:`(h_i,w_i,r_i)=(1,0,0)` denotes ``infected``, "
":math:`(h_i,w_i,r_i)=(1,1,0)` denotes ``weakened``."
msgstr ""
":math:`(h i,w i,r i)=(1,0)'表示“感染者”,math:`(h i,w i,r i)=(1,1,0)'表示“弱化”。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:68
#: 98eeb05b676648dd96b21cc0e2caf4f9
msgid ""
":math:`(h_i,w_i,r_i)=(0,0,1)` denotes ``recovered``, "
":math:`(h_i,w_i,r_i)=(0,0,0)` denotes ``susceptible``."
msgstr ":math:`(h i,w i,r i)=(0,0,1)'表示\"恢复\",\"(h i,w i,r i)=(0,0)\"表示\"可接受\"."

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:70
#: 6d642428128b41dd8e49d17c7858cbbc
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution"
msgstr "每个受感染的邻居:math:节点的`j':math:`i ' 传递日志概率贡献"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:72
#: 7db98396c4f64bf8a2c0c0c11e1a6b23
msgid ""
"For each edge :math:`j\\to i`, an infected neighbor contributes to the log-"
"survival; the per-step infection probability for node :math:`i` is"
msgstr "每个边缘:`j\\to i',感染的邻居对日志存活作出贡献;节点的每步感染概率:`i'是:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:74
#: 9bb2a54518194721b0f9bb71c774f80d
msgid ""
"m_{ji}^{(k)} = \\mathbf{1}\\!\\left(h_j^{(k-1)}=1 \\land w_j^{(k-1)}=0\\right) \\cdot \\log(1-\\kappa), \\qquad\n"
"I_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right),"
msgstr ""
"m {ji}^{(k)}=\\ mathbf{1}\\!\\左(h j^{(k-1)}\\land w j^{(k-1)\\0\\右)\\cdot\\log(1-\\kappa),\\qquad\n"
"I i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)}m {ji}^{(k)}\\右),"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:79
#: ac31dd5f6d8c4302afbf1552140b08c9
msgid "applied only to currently susceptible and not recovered nodes."
msgstr "仅适用于目前易发而不回收的节点。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:81
#: 81542f51554c4289a351a35d407f47fb
msgid "**Weakening (S→W)**"
msgstr "** 擦伤(S-W)**"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:83
#: 8e1aebb040df4af7a30433b8c367adc5
msgid "Analogously, the probability to become weakened is"
msgstr "类似地,被削弱的概率是"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:85
#: 4d11d282aaca4ea79decfbc8e082989f
msgid ""
"\\widetilde{m}_{ji}^{(k)} = \\mathbf{1}\\!\\left(h_j^{(k-1)}=1 \\land w_j^{(k-1)}=0\\right) \\cdot \\log(1-\\mu), \\qquad\n"
"W_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} \\widetilde{m}_{ji}^{(k)} \\right),"
msgstr ""
"\\ glassintilde{ m} {ji}^{(k)} =\\ mathbf{1}\\!\\ 左 (h j^{(k-1)}\\land w j^{(k-1)}\\cdot\\log(1-\\mu),\\qquad\n"
"W i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)}\\glasstilde{m} {ji}^{(k)}\\右),"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:90
#: 8e6237ac29ae4f009ea4e5f25a81cd99
msgid "again only for nodes that are susceptible and not recovered."
msgstr "也只针对易发而不恢复的节点。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:92
#: 0f1b704c6984422b921a81924d8824ab
msgid "**Weakened to infected (W→I)**"
msgstr "** 被感染(W I)**"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:94
#: 9caf559ccd97464e9443d4a6274d073a
msgid ""
"A weakened node may become infected via infected neighbors with rate "
":math:`\\nu`:"
msgstr "一个弱小的节点可能会被感染,"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:96
#: 3054d18efa4e4812b94ce656c7a2ca7b
msgid ""
"\\widehat{m}_{ji}^{(k)} = \\mathbf{1}\\!\\left(h_j^{(k-1)}=1 \\land w_j^{(k-1)}=0\\right) \\cdot \\log(1-\\nu), \\qquad\n"
"WI_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} \\widehat{m}_{ji}^{(k)} \\right),"
msgstr ""
"\\ gladhat{ m} {ji}^{(k)} =\\ mathbf{ 1}\\!\\ 左 (h j^{(k-1)}\\ land w j^{(k-1)}\\ cdot\\log(1-\\nu),\\qquad\n"
"======================================================"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:101
#: 13308d66b9994780b21aed2c227e34f4
msgid "applied only to currently weakened nodes (:math:`w_i^{(k-1)}=1`)."
msgstr "仅适用于目前被削弱的节点(:math:`w i^{(k-1)}=1')。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:103
#: 78d92beb415e48d3893694923f4d41d4
msgid "**Recovery (I→R)**"
msgstr "** 复原(I R)**"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:105
#: 60ad84a3a27348c1816934c7dcba3e28
msgid ""
"In this implementation, infected and not-weakened nodes deterministically "
"recover at each step (no parameter :math:`\\gamma`). We model this as"
msgstr "在这一实施中,每个步骤(没有参数:math:QQgamma`)都会被感染且未微弱的节点确定恢复。 我们模拟这个"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:107
#: bbfa16c575634601a73278350d541d60
msgid ""
"r_i^{(k)} = r_i^{(k-1)} \\;\\lor\\; \\big( h_i^{(k-1)} = 1 \\land "
"w_i^{(k-1)} = 0 \\big),"
msgstr "r i^{(k)}= r i^{(k-1)}\\;\\lor\\;\\big(h i^{(k-1))}= 1\\land w(k-1)}=0\\big),"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:111
#: d5c8d6b05ebd43b3a33607d6bc683232
msgid ""
"and recovered nodes remain immune: they neither get weakened nor re-"
"infected."
msgstr "并且恢复的节点仍然保持免疫力:它们既不被削弱,也不被再次感染。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:113
#: dac5354430f945808d6179e587f109d2
