msgstr "** 抽样和状态更新**"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:115
#: 930098e632be4b78a9a40ae72f808cd4
msgid ""
"Let :math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{wk}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{wi}} \\sim"
" \\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)` be independent. The indicators are updated as"
msgstr ""
"让 : math: 'U i^{\\ mathrm{inf}}, U i^{\\ mathrm{wk}}, U i^{\\ "
"mathrm{wi}}\\sim\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)' 独立. 这些指标更新为:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SWIR.rst:117
#: 58e327a3bc7c4fd98df6ed0b6ec45d9b
